Who Do You Think You Are? Australia - Series 7, Episode 4




David Wenham

Actor David Wenham has inhabited countless characters in a 30 year career spanning theatre, TV and film but the characters in David's own bloodline remain largely unknown to him. Delving into the mystery behind his father's fostered childhood, David uncovers tales of horror and valour in the trenches of Gallipoli and the Somme, the double life of a homecoming hero, and a mother's struggle to stay connected to her son.




Original Air Date: 25-Aug-2015
